# Monorepo Dependency Guard

When modifying `package.json` or importing between packages:
1. Ensure no Circular Dependencies (e.g., `fhir-engine` -> `symphony` -> `fhir-engine`).
2. Use workspace protocol `workspace:*` for internal monorepo dependencies.
3. Always check if new code should belong in `shared-types` if used in more than one package.
